message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲! 🎊

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲! 🎊

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲! 🎊

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
